sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant B as Browser
    participant API as FastAPI
    participant Cache as Redis Cache
    participant Bus as Redis Pub/Sub
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant Search as Search Index
    participant Notif as Notification Worker

    B->>+API: POST /api/v1/trees/{tree_id}/persons {name, birth_date, ...}
    API->>API: Validate request (Pydantic schema)
    API->>API: Resolve tenant_id from JWT
    API->>API: Check permissions (RBAC: requires contributor+)

    Note over API,DB: Write path (Command side of CQRS)
    API->>+DB: BEGIN TRANSACTION
    DB-->>API: tx_id
    API->>DB: INSERT INTO persons (tenant_id, tree_id, ...)
    DB-->>API: person_id
    API->>DB: INSERT INTO audit_log (action=CREATE, entity=person, ...)
    API->>DB: COMMIT
    DB-->>-API: success

    Note over API,Cache: Cache invalidation
    API->>Cache: DEL tree:{tree_id}:summary
    API->>Cache: DEL search:{tenant_id}:persons:*

    Note over API,Bus: Domain event emission
    API->>Bus: PUBLISH domain.person.created {person_id, tree_id, tenant_id, actor_id}

    API-->>-B: 201 {person_id, created_at}

    Note over Bus,Notif: Async event handlers (decoupled)
    Bus->>Search: SUBSCRIBE domain.person.created → update_search_index(person_id)
    Search->>DB: SELECT person for indexing
    Search->>DB: UPDATE persons SET ts_vector = to_tsvector(...)

    Bus->>Notif: SUBSCRIBE domain.person.created → notify_collaborators
    Notif->>DB: SELECT collaborators for tree_id
    Notif->>Notif: Send in-app + email notifications
